    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition at $34,500, and that price is an honest reflection of what you're getting. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains good color and shine with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use. There are no major dents or rust concerns, though close inspection will reveal the small imperfections you'd expect from a well-used vehicle. The interior is clean and functional, with upholstery showing moderate wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and door panels, but no tears or significant damage. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and suspension \u2014 are in good working order, and the car drives confidently. It has been maintained adequately, though it is not a showroom-fresh example. This is a solid, reliable vehicle for a buyer seeking dependable everyday transportation without paying a premium for perfection.",
