    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with potential buyers about what to expect. The exterior shows significant wear including multiple dents, scratches, and faded or peeling paint in several areas. The interior has seen heavy use, with worn and torn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require attention \u2014 it runs, but is not in reliable daily-driver shape without some repair work. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project vehicle, or a buyer who needs the most basic point-A-to-point-B transportation and is prepared to invest in repairs. There are no recent major service records to offer, and the vehicle is priced accordingly to reflect its current state. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises hidden in the fine print.",
      "price": 4500.0,
